    "ideation": "The name badge emoji represents an identity held out for inspection—a mix of formal introduction, polite readiness, and the slight awkwardness of being a 'labeled' entity. The performance personifies the badge as a character entering a room: first a blank, stiff slate (representing the empty white field), then a self-aware moment of presenting its 'name' with a proud but rigid smile. The eyes act as the rounded cut-outs of the tulip-shaped badge, starting neutral and widening as it introduces itself. The mouth moves from a flat, clinical line to a professional, social-register curve. Color is themed around the classic red-and-white of the 1F4DB glyph, ending in a crisp, high-contrast state that feels like a clean sticker freshly applied.",
